            <p class="line"></p>
            <p class="text">
                &emsp;&emsp;Tuanshan Folk Residences is located on the border of Yunnan, surrounded by green mountain peaks, which is the best
                background color for the village. It is isolated from the rest of the world. After 600 years of wind and rain, most of
                the ancient buildings are well preserved and are listed as "World Architectural Heritage". Surrounded by mountains of
                mountains, the scenery here is perfect for people. Not only can you enjoy the beautiful natural landscape within the
                village, but you can also choose to explore the nearby natural environment on foot or on foot. Especially in the early
                morning and dusk, the interplay of light and shadow on the mountain peaks is definitely worth seeing.
            </p>
            <!--点赞-->
        </div>
